<div id="signing">
	<div class="callToAction">
		Stop Rewriting. Start Refactoring.
	</div>
	<div class="callToSignUp">
		To date, a total of <%= @signatories.size %> people have signed this manifesto. We have done so to voice our concern over the state of practice and our passion towards the profession of software development. We want to feel proud of our work and see our products stand the test of time, serving their users and developers alike.
	</div>
	<div class="signUpForm">
		<form id="signup_form" method="post" action="/signatories">
			<input class="text" type="text" name="name" />
			<input type="submit" name="sign" value="sign!" id="signup_button" />
		</form>
		<% if @added %>
		<div class="uxFeedback">Thanks for joining us. Your name, '<%= @added %>' will be listed among our signatories shortly.</div>
		<% end %>
	</div>
</div>
<div id="signatories">
	<h2>The following people have signed this manifesto:</h2>
	<ol class="signatories">
		<% @signatories.each_with_index do |signee, index| %>
		<li value="<%= @signatories.size - index %>"><span class="signatoryName"><%= signee.name %></span> <span class="signatoryDate">signed on <%= signee.created_at.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %></span></li>
		<% end %>
	</ol>
	<a class="backToTop" href="#top">Back to top</a>
</div>
